Enum Class Printer

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Printer>
Printer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Printer>, Constable
public enum Printer extends Enum<Printer>
A Java Print dependency for easy debugging, uses the default System.out PrintStream.

Methods like setAutoFlush(boolean) will alter the global state of System.out.

Sub-components:

  • Printer.Chrono
  • Printer.Export
  • Printer.Editor
